â‹ Energy Saving: Walton Intelligent Inverter Air Conditioner has got a unique feature named Economy. Just pressing a single button (ECO) will allow the unit to save up to 70% of energy compared to the typical non-inverter-type air conditioner. 

â‹ Silent Operation: Walton Intelligent Inverter Air Conditioner has a much quieter and smoother operation than the non-inverter type due to BLDC motor usage. Walton Intelligent Inverter Air Conditioner does its function smoothly and silently so that you can enjoy your peaceful sleep.

â‹ Fast Cooling: Compressor and control board are coupled in such a way that Walton Intelligent Inverter Air Conditioner offers fast cooling by just pressing a single button (Turbo) of the remote control. Now you can get cooled faster than ever. 

â‹ Multi-Directional Airflow- Walton Intelligent Inverter Air Conditioner has horizontal and vertical swing which enable the air to swing in four directions. You will feel the same comfort at every corner of the room. 

â‹ Wide Temperature range- Walton Intelligent Inverter Air Conditioner has a working temperature range of 16-31 degrees Celsius. 

â‹ Wide Working Voltage Range- Walton Intelligent Inverter Air Conditioner has a wide working voltage range starting from 140V to 264VAC 50Hz. 
Turn that hot, sweating, and tired day of yours into a cool and relaxing one with Waltonâ€™s Best AC in Bangladesh.

description:
#bengali #durgapuja2022, #durgapuja, #houstontx, #durgapujainus, #houstondurgabari, #ISKONofhouston

We started our Texas road trip series with our spring long weekend trip to the most important city of Northwestern Texas as well as Texas Panhandled, Amarillo. We also visited the grand canyon of Texas, Palo Duo Canyon, which is situated nearby Amarillo. This time we went to Houston for Durga Puja which is the most important festival of Bengali community. We made the weekend trip to Houston from Dallas on 30th September, 2022. We also went to Galveston from Houston on the next day which is 1st October, 2022 but we will share that video later. In this current video we share our happy experience of visiting two Bengali Durga puja in Houston where we meet some of our dearest friends whom we know before. Viewers would have a glimpse of the warmth of typical Bengali Durga puja that we used to have in Kolkata. We enjoyed a lot and hope that you would do the same.
